title: #114 - Endgame Review, KFC Ruins H3 Podcast, Fast Food Power Rankings
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we discuss our new arch nemesis Colonel Douchebag, draft our fast food power tier list, get a report on Ian's pilgrimage to see Kanye at Coachella, Hila reviews fan submitted terrible tattoos, and we discuss Avengers: Endgame (spoiler warning!)
